    {
      "text": "// Good: Use interpolation\nd`Hello ${userName}`;\n```\n\n### Don't Forget Newlines in Lists\n\n```typescript\n// Bad: Items will run together\nd`${items.map((item) =\u003e d`${item.name}`)}`;\n\n// Good: Explicit newlines\nd`${items.map((item) =\u003e d`${item.name}\\n`)}`;\n```\n\n### Don't Return Plain Strings\n\n```typescript\n// Bad: Plain string\nview() {\n  return \"Hello\"; // Won't work!\n}\n\n// Good: Use d template\nview() {\n  return d`Hello`;\n}\n```\n\n### Don't Mutate State in View\n\n```typescript\n// Bad: Side effects\nview() {\n  this.state.viewCount++; // Never do this!\n  return d`Viewed ${this.state.viewCount} times`;\n}\n\n// Good: Pure view\nview() {\n  return d`Viewed ${this.state.viewCount} times`;\n}\n```",
      "contextualizedText": "// Good: Use interpolation\nd`Hello ${userName}`;\n```\n\n### Don't Forget Newlines in Lists\n\n```typescript\n// Bad: Items will run together\nd`${items.map((item) =\u003e d`${item.name}`)}`;\n\n// Good: Explicit newlines\nd`${items.map((item) =\u003e d`${item.name}\\n`)}`;\n```\n\n### Don't Return Plain Strings\n\n```typescript\n// Bad: Plain string\nview() {\n  return \"Hello\"; // Won't work!\n}\n\n// Good: Use d template\nview() {\n  return d`Hello`;\n}\n```\n\n### Don't Mutate State in View\n\n```typescript\n// Bad: Side effects\nview() {\n  this.state.viewCount++; // Never do this!\n  return d`Viewed ${this.state.viewCount} times`;\n}\n\n// Good: Pure view\nview() {\n  return d`Viewed ${this.state.viewCount} times`;\n}\n```",
